Blake Goodman, PC, Bankruptcy & Debt Settlement Attorneys is a Hawai‘i-based Professional Corporation led by founding attorney Blake Goodman. Headquartered in Honolulu, Hawaii, the firm focuses exclusively on consumer insolvency and related debt-relief work. Its services include:  

• Chapter 7 bankruptcy filings to obtain complete discharge of unsecured debts;  
• Chapter 13 bankruptcy plan preparation and court representation to restructure and repay debts over three-to-five years;  
• Out-of-court debt settlement and negotiation with credit-card companies, medical providers, and other creditors;  
• Tax debt relief strategies that time filings to wipe out older IRS liabilities;  
• Foreclosure defense and mortgage modification assistance.  

These offerings are marketed as an integrated path to a “fresh start” for Hawai‘i residents burdened by overwhelming debt. [1][2]

